		"description": {
			"value": "<p><em>Rod - Very Rare</em></p><p><strong>Action</strong></p><ul><li><p>Activate the rod to transport yourself and up to 199 willing creatures you can see to a demiplane of your design. The demiplane provides food, water, and a safe environment; objects created there cannot leave.</p></li><li><p>Each hour spent there heals a visitor as though it had spent 1 Hit Die, and visitors do not age while within the demiplane. They can remain up to 200 days divided by the number of creatures present (round down).</p></li><li><p>When the time expires or you end the effect as an Action, every creature reappears in (or near) the space it left. Once used, this property can't be used again until 10 days have passed.</p></li></ul><section id=\"foundry-secret-1\" class=\"secret\"><p><strong>Foundry Note</strong></p><p>The <strong>Transport to Demiplane</strong> activity will consume a use of this item but the ten day recovery period must be tracked manually.</p></section>",
